### Radial Gradients for Focus
```svg
<radialGradient id="focus-gradient" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#58a6ff" stop-opacity="0.3" />
  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#58a6ff" stop-opacity="0.0" />
</radialGradient>
```

### Multi-Stop Gradients for Depth
```svg
<linearGradient id="depth-gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#21262d" />
  <stop offset="25%" stop-color="#161b22" />
  <stop offset="75%" stop-color="#0d1117" />
  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#010409" />
